## ⚙️ Installation

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/your-repository.git
```

Navigate to the project folder:

```bash
cd your-repository
```

Install dependencies:

```bash
npm install
```

Start the development server:

```bash
npm start
```

